\b \fs32 Layer 5 Design: Testing and Automation \b0\fs22\par
\par
Date: 2026-03-02\par
Layer: Testing/Automation\par
Depends on: all layers\par
\par
\b \fs28 1) Objective \b0\fs22\par
Validate full solution via unit, contract, integration, and BDD regression.\par
\par
\b \fs28 2) Existing BDD Scope \b0\fs22\par
Feature: `tests/integration/features/demo_qa_healing.feature`\par
- TC1: text-box fill + submit\par
- TC2: checkbox Home icon select + message verify\par
- TC3: webtables first-row verification\par
- TC4: intentional negative raw invalid fallback xpath\par
\par
\b \fs28 3) Testing Code Graph \b0\fs22\par
\par
\par
pytest -> unit tests (core/store/rag)\par
pytest-bdd -> integration steps\par
  -> Playwright browser/page fixtures\par
  -> XPathHealerFacade recover calls\par
  -> artifacts (screenshots/videos/reports/logs/metadata)\par
\par
\par
\b \fs28 4) Commands (Canonical) \b0\fs22\par
\par
\b \fs24 4.1 Compile check \b0\fs22\par
\par
python -m compileall -q .\par
\par
\par
\b \fs24 4.2 Unit tests \b0\fs22\par
\par
python -m pytest -q tests\\unit\par
\par
\par
\b \fs24 4.3 Integration BDD \b0\fs22\par
\par
python -m pytest -q -rs -m integration tests\\integration\\test_demo_qa_healing_bdd.py --cucumberjson=artifacts/reports/cucumber.json\par
\par
\par
Expected baseline:\par
- `3 passed`\par
- `1 failed` (intentional TC4 negative)\par
