\par
\b \fs28 6) Exact Implementation Prompt (Testing) \b0\fs22\par
\par
Implement full testing stack for xpath-healer.\par
1) Keep unit tests for core/store/rag modules.\par
2) Keep pytest-bdd integration feature with TC1..TC4.\par
3) Ensure broken fallback xpath is used to trigger healer in positive scenarios.\par
4) Ensure step screenshots and one video per test are captured.\par
5) Generate junit, cucumber json, steps jsonl, healing-calls jsonl, and custom html report.\par
6) Keep TC4 as intentional negative scenario to demonstrate raw xpath failure reporting.\par
7) Add contract tests for PG repository and API response schemas.\par
\par
\par
\b \fs28 7) Release Exit Criteria \b0\fs22\par
- All non-negative tests green.\par
- No high-severity defects open.\par
- Logs and reports include traceability from request to healed locator.\par
